*% --------------- Custom Page Sizes ---------------

*NonUIOrderDependency: 220.0 DocumentSetup *CustomPageSize
*CustomPageSize True: "
    /SHOptions /ProcSet resourcestatus
        {
        pop pop userdict /SHPlugInSettings 2 copy known {get exec}{pop pop} ifelse
        pop pop pop 0 3 1 roll
        3 array astore
        /CustomPageSize /SHOptions /ProcSet findresource /setSHOptions get exec
        }
        {
        pop pop pop
        2 array astore << /PageSize 3 -1 roll >> setpagedevice
        }
    ifelse"
*End

*% Minimum:  90 x 148 mm
*% Maximum: 316 x 550 mm
*ParamCustomPageSize Width: 1 points 255.11 895.75
*ParamCustomPageSize Height: 2 points 419.52 1559.06
